{"tid":2138112,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"繼DNA後 香港人嘅信貸資料都極有可能會送中","createTime":"2020-08-03T11:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T08:55:26.000Z","uid":155674,"like":93,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1f38c79fd7f4f3255a3e7e2c8930cb5e848ca7","tid":2138112,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">TLDR: 本身香港嘅唯一信態評級機構係美資公司<br />\n但黎緊金管局會招標，有幾間中資背景嘅公司已經決定左會參與<br />\n換句話講，香港人嘅信態評級會同DNA一樣直接送中</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】由金管局發功，銀行公會推動，在港成立多於一間個人信貸資料庫（CRA）、打破環聯資訊獨市經營路線圖初步落實。消息透露，銀公上周三與業界舉行簡報會，11月邀請有意競投機構交建議書；傳聞平保（2318）旗下金融壹賬通有興趣參與。<br />\n<br />\n現有CRA經營者環聯及諾華誠信外，金融壹賬通亦被指有興趣，是否入標仍待觀察；若三間均競投並勝出，意味日後掌管全港個人信貸資料的營運商，最少兩間與中資有密切聯繫或直屬中資機構。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200803/XNILJCDAWTUHG53QZYNKHRFTGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200803%2FXNILJCDAWTUHG53QZYNKHRFTGM%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0OxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=53f688e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200803%2FXNILJCDAWTUHG53QZYNKHRFTGM%2F&h=f1c64bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200803/XNILJCDAWTUHG53QZYNKHRFTGM/</a>"},{"pid":"8250f0ab4abe4514c8c1e840488301779e2467da","tid":2138112,"uid":151439,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"留島又留人 <br />\n人都癲  香港版社會徵信系統 不是夢"},{"pid":"8523c61cb39f0c4467ef56f7961805ff634b0d07","tid":2138112,"uid":7179,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"信貸資料送中＝支那知道邊啲有錢人唔走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9544870bb22d75b37f86e46554723f098569fd3","tid":2138112,"uid":111448,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbda200e1a90ec5695269f701acef065748a7a69","tid":2138112,"uid":1