0-08-03T11:36:08.000Z","msg":"你tu幾多？"},{"pid":"346a123c01dcdbff75e59621febefb6bb9429ead","tid":2138112,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bef435304a33d421ee3568b5d29900139d5b7d5","tid":2138112,"uid":269527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"失信人士 揮手區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"第一時間送你中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78893a9d8ce95b77a227a96b1e4f775a5e29c80","tid":2138112,"uid":269527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f9544870bb22d75b37f86e46554723f098569fd3","tid":2138112,"uid":111448,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 金管局賣港有很多方法<br />\n【畢打街閒人】環聯信貸背後跟中資的博奕衝突（渾水）｜壹週刊<br />\n這些大數據和信貸紀錄，只要結合銀行反洗黑錢的資本流動足印，一旦加以數據化運用，國家想查中港兩地邊個走資、洗黑錢和漏稅都無問題。范冰冰逃稅案的餘溫，盛載住當權者打貪捉鬼的意識形態，已經在商業層次中體現出來了。<br />\n現在是不是可以用更高維度去理解，點解馬雲要買美國萬通，那堆data太值錢，而且配合國策可以做到政治戰略目的。這跟諾華誠信打環聯一樣，都是同樣的邏輯貫穿，以前不知道這些離散數據有咩用，大數據年代後大家都知道了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_647524_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_647524_0&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0OxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=c427029a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_647524_0&h=def029f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_647524_0</a>"},{"pid":"64fe2180140dc78447bb0a00fd220484c2f23fb1","tid":2138112,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbda200e1a90ec5695269f701acef065748a7a69","tid":2138112,"uid":1