:"87bffb5880807f6b9062dd2cc50fbdc68f165506","tid":2138112,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f1f38c79fd7f4f3255a3e7e2c8930cb5e848ca7","tid":2138112,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">TLDR: 本身香港嘅唯一信態評級機構係美資公司<br />\n但黎緊金管局會招標，有幾間中資背景嘅公司已經決定左會參與<br />\n換句話講，香港人嘅信態評級會同DNA一樣直接送中</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】由金管局發功，銀行公會推動，在港成立多於一間個人信貸資料庫（CRA）、打破環聯資訊獨市經營路線圖初步落實。消息透露，銀公上周三與業界舉行簡報會，11月邀請有意競投機構交建議書；傳聞平保（2318）旗下金融壹賬通有興趣參與。<br />\n<br />\n現有CRA經營者環聯及諾華誠信外，金融壹賬通亦被指有興趣，是否入標仍待觀察；若三間均競投並勝出，意味日後掌管全港個人信貸資料的營運商，最少兩間與中資有密切聯繫或直屬中資機構。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200803/XNILJCDAWTUHG53QZYNKHRFTGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200803%2FXNILJCDAWTUHG53QZYNKHRFTGM%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0OxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=53f688e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200803%2FXNILJCDAWTUHG53QZYNKHRFTGM%2F&h=f1c64bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200803/XNILJCDAWTUHG53QZYNKHRFTGM/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"咁咪只用外資銀行信用咭囉。<br />\n<br />\n中資未日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5baab0721dcd8899f04d0e9e0084b2c375ab7733","tid":2138112,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23a49a1a2c78661041e08c5d6939a862ca22c718","tid":2138112,"uid":151439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:16:48.000Z","msg":"以後唔駛join 自願器官捐贈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"關咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bcfdd18d08dfb53d9f972444531240878ac959","tid":2138112,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b8e3f88e10821ff3945e771d957f90be6df09b8","tid":2138112,"uid":63057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score